articles.title: The fascinating coaching matchup of Oregon’s Dan Lanning and Indiana’s Curt Cignetti - OregonLive.com
articles.description: Lanning and Cignetti bring contrasting backgrounds but similar philosophies to Saturday's Big Ten showdown, with both teams looking to strengthen their playoff positioning.
articles.content:
EUGENE Two of the top teams, led by two of the best coaches in the Big Ten will square off at Autzen Stadium when Dan Lanning and No. 3 Oregon host Curt Cignetti and No. 7 Indiana.
